{"id":"f32baed6-a430-4246-ace4-1152c237532e","name":"Garrick || Big Bad Wolf","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Who's afraid of the big bad wolf?</em><br><br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You shouldn't have gone into the woods after dark..</strong>.<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Don’t go into the woods after sundown— you’ve heard it your entire life.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">There’s a fearsome wolf demi-human that lives there and he’ll eat your heart if he catches you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>But you’re all grown up now.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>So you think nothing of taking the shortcut through the woods. <br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">After all, it’s just an old legend told to children to keep them from wandering off <em>right?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You’re not one to be scared—</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">That is until you feel an intense gaze upon you– and the sense of dread permeating every fiber of your being. <br><br>Someone is stalking you through these woods.<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Perhaps you should have been afraid of the big bad wolf…</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FIGZCPtRLKY7Qmb-Mz00L.webp\" style=\"width: 267px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>This bot deals with stalking, possessive behavior, marking, biting, potential blood, etc. Also, theres knots 'cause.... wolf.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UBiBBU-Lq0Jj8mFUMTB07.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 658px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXpTzFmxBTnj8TiZJQeVS.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 332px;\"><br>A common theme for me lately has been how bad work has been so my halloween bots have gotten a little lost in the shuffle. <br><br>I promised Garrick to my server like three weeks ago but never managed to finish him. <br><br>The plan was to have him out monday but... work crashed and burned hard. <br><br>Here's to november not being as much of a shit show of a month.<br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zb9-ZUgzPVVpYYwIA37OQ.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 405px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 183, 112);\"><strong><em><u>W</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 178, 103);\"><strong><em><u>a</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 174, 95);\"><strong><em><u>n</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 169, 86);\"><strong><em><u>t</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 164, 78);\"><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 159, 69);\"><strong><em><u>m</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 155, 61);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 150, 52);\"><strong><em><u>r</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 147, 43);\"><strong><em><u>e</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 143, 35);\"><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 140, 26);\"><strong><em><u>M</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 136, 17);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 133, 9);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 129, 0);\"><strong><em><u>n</u></em></st","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"we9ox3WyAXPs4k6XhHnyD.webp","creator":"m00nprincess","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":6169,"messages":140496,"created_at":"2025-10-31T01:46:59.172438+00:00"}